
.venv\Scripts\activate
cd project
pip install -r requirements.txt
2. Start Backend API (Terminal 1)
cd project
uvicorn api.server:app --host 127.0.0.1 --port 8000
3. Start Voice Agent (Terminal 2)
cd project
python agent/livekit_agent.py dev
4. Start Frontend (Terminal 3)
cd frontend
npm start
5. Test in Browser

Open http://localhost:3000
Join a room
Talk to the agent


or

1. One-Click Start
Double-click the "start_app.bat" file in this folder.

This will automatically:
- Start the Backend API (Terminal 1)
- Start the Voice Agent (Terminal 2)
- Start the Frontend (Terminal 3)
- Open your browser to http://localhost:3000

Just wait for all windows to appear and the browser to open!



